<h1 class="tagline" align="center"><!--p class="tagline"-->40th anniversary celebration of the Arnold Klein Gallery!<!--/p--></h1>
<h2>Valentine's Day, 2011</h2>
<p>
The physical gallery closed its doors on Valentine's Day, 2011, after 40 years in business in Royal Oak, Michigan, but the Arnold Klein Gallery will continue its online operations!  
<br />
This event was covered by different online venues:
<br /><br />
